product.title: Shark Cat and Buddies Tee
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Feelin' fishy? 

    Our Shark Cat and Buddies Tee will have you lookin' sharp in no time! This fun and fashionable t-shirt features everyone's favorite ocean villains - Shark Cat and his buddies - sure to put a smile on even the grumpiest face! Don't miss your chance to show your shark pride!

    Available in six different sizes, measurements are shown below. We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.

    Size (inches) S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 41 41 42 42 44 48
    Length 25 26 26 26 28 27
                 
    Size (cm) S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 104 106 107 108 110 140
    Length 65 66 66 67 67 81


    Features

    🍙 50% Premium Polyester & 50% Cotton
    🍙 Short oversized sleeves

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.


  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
